description: El Saborsito Tejano is serving up San Antonio amazingly delicious made from scratch Mexican cuisine. With yummy breakfast tacos, and a selection of burritos, tacos, tortas, and more, with your choice of flavorful meats, from carne asada to el pastor, it’s no wonder that this bright, lively truck is a local favorite. If you wish to embellish your next meal or event with tasty flavors and friendly service, El Saborsito Tejano is certainly the truck for you.
name: El Saborsito Tejano
